==Portuguese==
Girafa is a developer and provider of data [[visualization]] solutions and services, designed to simplify, enhance and improve the experience of Information [[Search]] and Web navigation. Using Girafa's technology end users are able to view [[thumbnail]] sized images of any hyperlink they choose on the web, instantly, without the time-consuming task of waiting for each page to load. The ability to immediately preview a Web site or document brings simplicity, productivity and efficiency to the WWW browsing and search experience.

Girafa's [[thumbnails]] have been used in numerous different applications, ranging from [[Windows Explorer]] to Internet [[search engines]] and web directories which provide a thumbnail preview of a webpage alongside search results.

*[http://www.girafa.com Girafa.com]

